
   This mud is still under construction, and thus there may still be
   some bugs within the game. Ideas and bug reports are always 
   welcome, but feel free to log on and look around, and enjoy the
   world that's being created.


   Please note that to prevent your character from being deleted, you
   must log in at least once every 30 days if you are under 1 day old.
   For more specifics on the deletion times please consult 'help age'.


